title: Egypt protests
name: Egypt protests
description:
The protests in Egypt are rumbling on, these are the hotspots around the country.

Compiled by Storyful.com.

properties.description: The presidential palace in this district was reportedly under siege.

properties.description: Reports of police lines were overpowered in minutes, police station occupied.
